All issues of the Journal of the American Mathematical Society 1988-1995

MYRIAD WAREZ, the world's foremost warez organization specialising in
mathematical research papers, is proud to present every paper published in the
Journal of the AMS between Volume 1 (1988) and Volume 8 (1995). Since Volumes 9
onward are freely available at http://www.ams.org/jams/ this now makes all 
issues of the world's most frequently cited mathematical journal accessible
to anyone with an Internet connection.

IF you have access to mathematical research papers which are not free to all
on the Net..
IF you can supply institutional logins for MYRIAD to use..
IF you can set up a proxy inside your institution's IP space to download

IF you can provide ftp mirrors or irc bots to use in distributing papers..
IF you know how to delete watermarks and other identifying data from pdf
files..
IF you can advise MYRIAD as to which papers and journals in your field of 
mathematics are the most important targets..
